author: wrowe
msg: The .36 release.  Kill the seperate .log/.conf types and associate both
types with txtfile (configured as Notepad by default on nearly any
Windows install.)  I'm not happy with this solution (we need to reconsider
this approach entirely) but it's a stop-gap that assures we work around
the REG_EXPAND_SZ bug in tracking down %SystemRoot%.
Also drop the OPENSSL-LICENSE.txt which is simply incorporated into
LICENCE.txt if the Makefile.win is invoked and srclib/openssl exists.
